text:
1718 Richmond Road, at the S. E. corner of Naughton Avenue (between Buel and Stobe Avenues). The real estate atlases from 1874 to 1907 show the house to have been on the Seaver estate. In 1917 it is shown to be on property belonging to St. Anns Roman Catholic Church.

May 17, 1932

P. L. Sperr
